=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222270/extras/283b74d81d3f23f0491246fad63b26f4.apng?t=1726053119\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222270/extras/283b74d81d3f23f0491246fad63b26f4.poster.avif?t=1726053119\" class=\"bb_img\" width=20 height=20 /></picture></span> Use your shield to defend and your gun to attack! (Handy against knife wielding punks and crazed mutants)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222270/extras/283b74d81d3f23f0491246fad63b26f4.apng?t=1726053119\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222270/extras/283b74d81d3f23f0491246fad63b26f4.poster.avif?t=1726053119\" class=\"bb_img\" width=20 height=20 /></picture></span> Face your gun down to perform a ROCKET JUMP!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222270/extras/283b74d81d3f23f0491246fad63b26f4.apng?t=1726053119\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222270/extras/283b74d81d3f23f0491246fad63b26f4.poster.avif?t=1726053119\" class=\"bb_img\" width=20 height=20 /></picture></span> Epic Boss fights, including a thrilling chainsaw death match.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222270/extras/283b74d81d3f23f0491246fad63b26f4.apng?t=1726053119\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222270/extras/283b74d81d3f23f0491246fad63b26f4.poster.avif?t=1726053119\" class=\"bb_img\" width=20 height=20 /></picture></span> Unlock hidden levels opening a whole new perspective! can you find them all?<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1